SofaKing Android includes many features and modifications which extend the capabilities of Android.  With each update to Android, Sofa Kings features may change or be altered to work with the latest version.

Feature list (much more then we could ever list):
- The Power of Sloth 
- Ribbons (AOKP)
- Customizable Quick Settings
- Missed call breathing notifications
- App Ops access in Settings
- Battery Icon and Battery Bar Options
- Active Display (Moto X notifications)
- Custom System Animations
- Swipe to Switch in Nocturnal Tweaks
- DarkUI in Nocturnal Tweaks
- Lockscreen Icon Color Changer
- Weather Panel in Status Bar
- Much much more with many new features being added almost daily!
